    "view": {
      "representation": "view",
      "value": "<div class=\"confluence-information-macro confluence-information-macro-information conf-macro output-block\" data-hasbody=\"true\" data-macro-id=\"76200df1-9e02-4e47-bba4-e405093df890\" data-macro-name=\"info\"><span class=\"aui-icon aui-icon-small aui-iconfont-info confluence-information-macro-icon\"> </span><div class=\"confluence-information-macro-body\"><p>The following workflow is for H21.0 and above</p></div></div><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"RenderMan_Solaris_PortalLights.jpg\" width=\"760\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/567050268/RenderMan_Solaris_PortalLights.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1761651341276&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=760&amp;height=393\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/567050268/RenderMan_Solaris_PortalLights.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1761651341276&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"1323\" data-width=\"2554\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"634421471\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"RenderMan_Solaris_PortalLights.jpg\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/jpeg\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"567050268\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"4\" data-media-id=\"d594590d-ff3a-4340-ba65-12e57f561a4d\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/567050268/RenderMan_Solaris_PortalLights.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1761651341276&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=1520&amp;height=786 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/567050268/RenderMan_Solaris_PortalLights.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1761651341276&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=760&amp;height=393 1x\"></span><p>Since it is difficult for a renderer to resolve interiors with little or no direct lighting, portal lights help direct the renderer's attention to the exterior source of light. </p><p>To set up Portal Lights in Solaris requires the <em>portallight </em>LOP to be in the Solaris network before the domelight it will be attached to.</p><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"RenderMan_Solaris_PortalLights_network.jpg\" width=\"760\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/567050268/RenderMan_Solaris_PortalLights_network.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1761651552114&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=760&amp;height=357\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/567050268/RenderMan_Solaris_PortalLights_network.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1761651552114&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"661\" data-width=\"1406\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"634421480\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"RenderMan_Solaris_PortalLights_network.jpg\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/jpeg\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"567050268\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"4\" data-media-id=\"4d70455f-7a46-4fc3-ab67-60ced52704d8\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/567050268/RenderMan_Solaris_PortalLights_network.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1761651552114&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=1406&amp;height=661 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/567050268/RenderMan_Solaris_PortalLights_network.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1761651552114&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=760&amp;height=357 1x\"></span><p>Once created, it can then be attached to the domelight:</p><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"RenderMan_Solaris_PortalLights_network_domelight.jpg\" width=\"760\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/567050268/RenderMan_Solaris_PortalLights_network_domelight.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1761651657168&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=760&amp;height=334\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/567050268/RenderMan_Solaris_PortalLights_network_domelight.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1761651657168&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"737\" data-width=\"1674\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"634290423\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"RenderMan_Solaris_PortalLights_network_domelight.jpg\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/jpeg\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"567050268\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"4\" data-media-id=\"1f320e23-3c74-42e6-86b6-f18414c67594\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/567050268/RenderMan_Solaris_PortalLights_network_domelight.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1761651657168&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=1520&amp;height=668 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/567050268/RenderMan_Solaris_PortalLights_network_domelight.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1761651657168&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=760&amp;height=334 1x\"></span><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"RenderMan_Solaris_PortalLights_params.jpg\" width=\"760\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/567050268/RenderMan_Solaris_PortalLights_params.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1761651713175&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=760&amp;height=377\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/567050268/RenderMan_Solaris_PortalLights_params.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1761651713175&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"843\" data-width=\"1699\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"634290431\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"RenderMan_Solaris_PortalLights_params.jpg\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/jpeg\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"567050268\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"4\" data-media-id=\"ce81682c-8c4f-4fe7-b6ce-a0d06532776d\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/567050268/RenderMan_Solaris_PortalLights_params.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1761651713175&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=1520&amp;height=754 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/567050268/RenderMan_Solaris_PortalLights_params.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1761651713175&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=760&amp;height=377 1x\"></span><p>For more info on the parameters in the Portal Light, <a class=\"external-link\" href=\"https://rmanwiki-27.pixar.com/space/REN27/542228147/PxrPortalLight\" rel=\"nofollow\">here is the main page</a></p><p /><p /><p /><p /><p />"
